          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "REC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The energy distribution of the neutrons was",
                "obtained by observing a large number of recoil",
                "protons in a cloud chamber. From the stopping power",
                "of the gas in the chamber and the range-velocity",
                "curve, the energy of the recoil protons was computed."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "All observed tracks were counted, regardless of their",
                "orientation. When the voltage was increased from 0.5",
                "MeV to 0.9 MeV the average number of tracks per",
                "expansion increased from 2.7 to 42 with the Be target,",
                "and from 7.1 to 13.4 with the H3PO4 target. These",
                "data have been reduced to an absolute yield."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": 500.0,
                "maximum_value": 1000.0,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The relative yields are much",
                "more accurate than the absolute ones; the latter may",
                "be in error by as much as a factor of 5 or possibly 10."
              ]
            }
          ],
